title: Signs Point to China in US Research Facility Hack
text:
19 Signs Point to China in US Research Facility Hack 
Defense One: Tech companies, healthcare giants, defense contractors, top universities, the US government—you name it, Chinese cyber-spies have probably hacked it. And now, it seems likely, we can add one of the world’s preeminent marine research groups to the list.
